  <div id="text-content_ecfdea01-2377-4bf8-a81a-97e19406fc4e" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Feature Settings section, use the <strong>Disable Celebration Animations</strong> icon to enable or disable this feature. </p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> If the Disable Celebration Animations feature setting does not display, it has not been enabled by your institution. </p>
